\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ee9c b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 ai m\\u1edbi l&agrave;m quen v\\u1edbi DeFi \\u0111\\u1ec1u c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 tham gia m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n hi\\u1ec3u bi\\u1ebft s&acirc;u r\\u1ed9ng. Quy tr&igrave;nh tr\\u1ecf v&agrave; nh\\u1ea5p cho ph&eacute;p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u canh t&aacute;c v&agrave; th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c&aacute;c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c ph&acirc;n b\\u1ed5 nh&oacute;m c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch nhanh ch&oacute;ng v&agrave; d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>V&iacute; CeFi-Style.<\\/strong> Moonfarm kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n nhu c\\u1ea7u t\\u1ea3i th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng v&iacute; c\\u1ee7a b&ecirc;n th\\u1ee9 ba n\\u1eefa. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \\u0111&atilde; &aacute;p d\\u1ee5ng c&aacute;ch ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng CeFi nh\\u01b0 Binance v&agrave; Coinbase, cho ph&eacute;p m\\u1ed9t v&iacute; d\\u1ef1a tr&ecirc;n web \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0ng an to&agrave;n cao m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i nh\\u1edb ho\\u1eb7c l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef kh&oacute;a c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ho\\u1eb7c c\\u1ee5m t\\u1eeb h\\u1ea1t gi\\u1ed1ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>\\u0110a chu\\u1ed7i.<\\/strong> Moonfarm cung c\\u1ea5p quy\\u1ec1n truy c\\u1eadp v&agrave;o c&aacute;c nh&oacute;m nu&ocirc;i t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t tr&ecirc;n nhi\\u1ec1u chu\\u1ed7i kh\\u1ed1i. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t&aacute;c v\\u1edbi t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c&aacute;c blockchain ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xuy&ecirc;n b\\u1ed5 sung th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>C\\u1ecdc m\\u1ed9t m\\u1eb7t.<\\/strong> Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng Moonfarm c&oacute; t&ugrave;y ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ea3 m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o LP ho\\u1eb7c m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o \\u0111\\u01a1n l\\u1ebb. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng ki\\u1ebfm thu nh\\u1eadp th\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n cung c\\u1ea5p thanh kho\\u1ea3n cho m\\u1ed9t d\\u1ef1 &aacute;n, do \\u0111&oacute; tr&aacute;nh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p c\\u1ee7a vi\\u1ec7c cung c\\u1ea5p thanh kho\\u1ea3n c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 nguy c\\u01a1 m\\u1ea5t m&aacute;t ti\\u1ec1m t&agrave;ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>B\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7.<\\/strong> Moonfarm \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ec3m to&aacute;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng b\\u1edfi c&ocirc;ng ty ki\\u1ec3m to&aacute;n \\u0111\\u1ed9c l\\u1eadp Arcadia. H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng bao g\\u1ed3m nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1edbp b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1edfi c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt CNTT. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n&agrave;y bao g\\u1ed3m c&aacute;c quy tr&igrave;nh t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ph&aacute;t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u1ed7 h\\u1ed5ng b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt v&agrave; t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng d\\u1eebng t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c&aacute;c giao d\\u1ecbch n\\u1ebfu xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 t&iacute;n hi\\u1ec7u \\u0111&aacute;ng ng\\u1edd n&agrave;o. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng nhi\\u1ec1u ph&ecirc; duy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 chuy\\u1ec3n giao n\\u1ed9i b\\u1ed9 v&agrave; qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; t&agrave;i s\\u1ea3n, nh\\u1eb1m ng\\u0103n ch\\u1eb7n vi\\u1ec7c hack n\\u1ed9i b\\u1ed9. Moonfarm \\u0111&atilde; ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y k\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb khi th&agrave;nh l\\u1eadp m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed khai th&aacute;c.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Ph&iacute; r\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea5p. <\\/strong>Ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u0103ng l&ecirc;n cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng Moonfarm do ph&iacute; gas th\\u1ea5p tr&ecirc;n n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng c\\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i, c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf nhi\\u1ec1u giao d\\u1ecbch c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec3 g\\u1eedi v&agrave; r&uacute;t t&agrave;i s\\u1ea3n kh\\u1ecfi giao th\\u1ee9c DeFi \\u0111i\\u1ec3n h&igrave;nh.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng &aacute;p d\\u1ee5ng h&agrave;ng lo\\u1ea1t.<\\/strong> B\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf l\\u1edbp ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p li&ecirc;n quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn DeFi, gi&uacute;p n&acirc;ng cao n\\u0103ng su\\u1ea5t d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng nh\\u01b0 mua c\\u1ed5 phi\\u1ebfu, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn cao h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng, Moonfarm c&oacute; ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c &aacute;p d\\u1ee5ng h&agrave;ng lo\\u1ea1t.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"meta_title\":\"N\\u1ec1n T\\u1ea3ng CeDeFi\",\"meta_keywords\":\"CeDeFi,N\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng CeDeFi\",\"meta_description\":\"M\\u1ed9t n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng CeDeFi cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u h\\u00f3a n\\u0103ng su\\u1ea5t canh t\\u00e1c h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u00ean th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng.\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"CeDeFi Platform\",\"intro\":\"A CeDeFi platform that offers market leading yield farming optimization.\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"CeDeFi Platform\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/Cedefi.png\\\" style=\\\"height:100%; width:100%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">A CeDeFi platform that offers market leading yield farming optimization. By doing so, we will contribute to Bridge the gap between CeFi and DeFi; Remove entry barriers to yield farming and enhance users&rsquo; experience; Provide better capital utilization; Create strong optimization that provides the best benefits to DeFi users; Boost crypto adoption<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Moonfarm is a farming system that combines DeFi&rsquo;s high-yield APR with CeFi&rsquo;s ease of use.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>User Friendly. <\\/strong>Moonfarm&rsquo;s platform has been designed to be so straightforward that anyone who is new to DeFi can participate, without the need for an in-depth understanding. Point-and-click processes allow users to begin farming and make adjustments to their pool allocations quickly and easily.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>CeFi-Style Wallet. <\\/strong>The need to download additional third-party wallet apps is gone with Moonfarm. We have taken the same approach to CeFi platforms like Binance and Coinbase, allowing a simple yet highly secure web-based wallet without the need to remember or store private keys or seed phrases.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Multi-chain. <\\/strong>Moonfarm provides access to the best farming pools across multiple blockchains. We interact with all of the major blockchains and are regularly adding more to our service.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Single-sided staking.<\\/strong> Moonfarm users have the option of staking both LP tokens or single tokens. This enables users to earn passive income without the need to provide liquidity to a project, thereby avoiding the complexity of liquidity provision as well as the potential risk of impermanent loss.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Security. <\\/strong>Moonfarm has been successfully audited by independent auditing company Arcadia. The system consists of multiple layers of protection designed by IT security experts. This includes auto-detect vulnerability processes and auto-stop on all transactions if any suspicious signals appear. We have a multi-approval system for internal transferring and asset management, to prevent internal hacking. Moonfarm has operated daily since inception without a history of exploitation.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Very low fees.<\\/strong> Profit potential is increased for Moonfarm users due to low gas fees on our platform, along with the removal of many of the transactions required to deposit and withdraw assets from a typical DeFi protocol.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Potential for mass adoption.<\\/strong> By removing the complexity layer associated with DeFi, &nbsp;making yield farming as easy as buying stocks, whilst offering higher returns than traditional finance, Moonfarm has the potential for mass adoption.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"meta_title\":\"CeDeFi Platform\",\"meta_keywords\":\"CeDeFi\",\"meta_description\":\"A CeDeFi platform that offers market leading yield farming optimization.\"}}',	'2022-07-21 17:17:57',	'2022-07-21 17:17:57'),
(127,	'posts',	'updated',	307,	'Modules\\Article\\Entities\\Post',	2,	'App\\Models\\User',	'{\"attributes\":{\"intro\":\"M\\u1ed9t tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i b\\u1eafn s\\u00fang nh\\u1eadp vai d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 blockchain v\\u1edbi b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp v\\u0169 kh\\u00ed gi\\u00fap ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i trang b\\u1ecb, n\\u00e2ng c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 v\\u00e0 ki\\u1ebfm NFT & token.\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/meta strike.jpg\\\" style=\\\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">1. Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u1ec1 MetaStrike<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t d\\u1ef1 &aacute;n FPS Multiplayer Blockchain Game bao g\\u1ed3m nhi\\u1ec1u t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft v&agrave; n&acirc;ng cao c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i b\\u1eafn s&uacute;ng, v\\u1edbi l\\u1ed1i ch\\u01a1i hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v&agrave; s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 c&ocirc;ng s\\u1ee9c cao v\\u1ec1 c\\u1ea3 h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh v&agrave;<br \\/>\\r\\nc&aacute;ch ch\\u01a1i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">\\u0110i s&acirc;u v&agrave;o th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf sau th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng c\\u1ee7a CSGO v&agrave; Call of Duty. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 th\\u1ecfa m&atilde;n tr&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9 mang v&aacute;c c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t X&igrave; Trum! Tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti\\u1ec1n nhi\\u1ec7m FPS kh&aacute;c, b\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed3, v\\u1eadt ph\\u1ea9m v&agrave; s&uacute;ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf theo h&igrave;nh th\\u1ee9c c&acirc;n b\\u1eb1ng cao ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i chuy&ecirc;n nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Ngo&agrave;i ra, v&igrave; l&agrave; game blockchain n&ecirc;n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 giao d\\u1ecbch v\\u1eadt ph\\u1ea9m On-Chain, v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i s&uacute;ng v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1eadp nh\\u1eadt li&ecirc;n t\\u1ee5c. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n&agrave;y c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1eefu &iacute;ch cho nh\\u1eefng game th\\u1ee7 k\\u1ef3 c\\u1ef1u trong vi\\u1ec7c giao d\\u1ecbch v\\u1eadt ph\\u1ea9m hay s&uacute;ng \\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n minh b\\u1ea1ch v&agrave; \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u1edd c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 blockchain. Ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn s&uacute;ng AWM gi\\u1edbi h\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd r\\u1ea5t ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn tr&ecirc;n th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng NFT v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b&aacute;n t\\u1eeb chu\\u1ed7i n&agrave;y sang chu\\u1ed7i kh&aacute;c b\\u1edfi c&aacute;c tay s&uacute;ng b\\u1eafn t\\u1ec9a \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">T&Iacute;NH N\\u0102NG, \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Ch\\u01a1i mi\\u1ec5n ph&iacute; \\/ S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu: Kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i chi ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ec3 mua c&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9i \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ebfm ti\\u1ec1n: Hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t v&agrave; k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i ki\\u1ebfm \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th&ocirc;ng qua ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 PVE v&agrave; PVP.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">X&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ebfm ti\\u1ec1n: T&ugrave;y ch\\u1ec9nh b\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 c\\u1ee7a ri&ecirc;ng b\\u1ea1n, b&aacute;n ch&uacute;ng d\\u01b0\\u1edbi d\\u1ea1ng NFT trong Clan War (ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 bang h\\u1ed9i).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">2. Gameplay<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ea5u tr&uacute;c nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfn tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt s\\u1ed1 k\\u1ebft th&uacute;c m\\u1edf. Nh&oacute;m c\\u1ed1t l&otilde;i c\\u1ee7a Metastrike s\\u1ebd x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng cho c&aacute;c n\\u1ed9i dung tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c li&ecirc;n k\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u Metaverse theo s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng t&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. V\\u0169 tr\\u1ee5 Metastrike s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1 cao c&aacute;c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n v\\u1ec1 tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i, ch\\u1ee7 ngh\\u0129a hi\\u1ec7n th\\u1ef1c, gi\\u1ea3i tr&iacute; v&agrave; VR tr&ecirc;n h\\u1ebft; ch\\u1ec9 b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch c&oacute; tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ch\\u01a1i game phong ph&uacute;, h\\u1ec7 sinh th&aacute;i m\\u1edbi c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 thu h&uacute;t \\u0111\\u1ee7 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tham gia \\u0111\\u1ec3 t&iacute;ch l\\u0169y gi&aacute; tr\\u1ecb cho c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n chi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ea5u v\\u1edbi b\\u1ea1n b&egrave; v&agrave; k\\u1ebb th&ugrave; tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1t c&aacute;c ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i v&agrave; b\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn, lu&ocirc;n gi\\u1eef cho b\\u1ea1n \\u1edf v\\u1ecb tr&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng gi\\u1ed1ng ai. M\\u1ed9t trong \\u0111&oacute; ch\\u1ec9 c&oacute; k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n m\\u1edbi c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a tr\\u1eadn chi\\u1ebfn. Nh&oacute;m c\\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \\u0111&atilde; h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n h\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa v\\u1edbi c\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf ch\\u01a1i quen thu\\u1ed9c nh\\u01b0ng kh&aacute;c nhau bao g\\u1ed3m Ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u01a1n (PVE) v&agrave; Nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i (PVE &amp; PVP).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Khi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i m\\u1edbi b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i, h\\u1ecd s\\u1ebd ph\\u1ea3i ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh m\\u1ed9t kh&oacute;a \\u0111&agrave;o t\\u1ea1o \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 truy c\\u1eadp v&agrave;o c&aacute;c ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 ch\\u01a1i kh&aacute;c. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u01b0\\u1edfng (m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o, h\\u1ed9p NFT) b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh n&oacute;. Sau \\u0111&oacute;, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i s\\u1ebd t\\u1ea1o nh&acirc;n v\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh (th\\u1ebb chi ph&iacute; ho\\u1eb7c mi\\u1ec5n ph&iacute; l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u), m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i s\\u1ebd c&oacute; t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a 3 nh&acirc;n v\\u1eadt, m\\u1ed7i nh&acirc;n v\\u1eadt s\\u1ebd c&oacute; n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v&agrave; s\\u1ebd t\\u1ed1n n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u01a1i. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i s\\u1ebd nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ed9p NFT \\u0111\\u1ec3 m\\u1edf v&agrave; nh\\u1eadn m\\u1ed9t v\\u0169 kh&iacute; \\/ v\\u1eadt ph\\u1ea9m th&ocirc;ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u cu\\u1ed9c h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh. M\\u1ed7i ng&agrave;y, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i s\\u1ebd c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y (V&iacute; d\\u1ee5 10 l\\u1ea7n b\\u1eafn tr&uacute;ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u, 1 l\\u1ea7n h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3, ti&ecirc;u di\\u1ec7t b\\u1eb1ng s&uacute;ng ng\\u1eafn, v.v.), n&ecirc;n c\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh ch&uacute;ng v&agrave; nh\\u1eadn ph\\u1ea7n th\\u01b0\\u1edfng.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_keywords\":\"MetaStrike,Blockchain\",\"meta_description\":\"M\\u1ed9t tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i b\\u1eafn s\\u00fang nh\\u1eadp vai d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 blockchain v\\u1edbi b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp v\\u0169 kh\\u00ed gi\\u00fap ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i trang b\\u1ecb, n\\u00e2ng c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 v\\u00e0 ki\\u1ebfm NFT & token.\"},\"old\":{\"intro\":\"A blockchain-based role-play shooting game with a collection of weapons for players to equip, upgrade level to complete mission and earn NFT & tokens.\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/meta strike.jpg\\\" style=\\\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>1. About MetaStrike<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike is an FPS Multiplayer Blockchain Game project that includes many essential and advanced features of a shooting game, with modern gameplay and high effort investment in both visuals and<br \\/>\\r\\ngameplay.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Dive into a game world designed after the success of CSGO and Call of Duty. Players can satisfy their carrying level like a Smurf! The game is learned from other FPS predecessors, the maps, items, and guns are designed in a highly balanced form suitable for go-pro players.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">In addition, because it is a blockchain game, players can trade items On-Chain, with a variety of guns and constantly updated. This is extremely useful for veteran gamers in trading items or guns like traditional games but completely transparent and stable thanks to blockchain technology. Surely limited AWM guns will be very popular in the NFT marketplace and sold from chain to chain by high-class snipers!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">FEATURES<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Free to Play\\/ Own: No need to spend money to buy first squads.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Play to Earn: Performance and game results earn through PVE and PVP mode.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Build to Earn: Custom your own maps, sell them as NFT in Clan War (guild mode).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>2. Gameplay<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike is structured as an open-ended digital battlefield. The Metastrike core team will build functionality for the game assets associated with the Metaverse brand in concurrence with the community. The Metastrike universe will promote the elements of game expertise, realism, entertainment, and VR above all; only by having an immersive gaming experience can the ecosystem attract enough participants to accrue value to the community.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Metastrike lets you fight friends and enemies across an engaging array of game modes and maps, always keeping you on the edge of your seat like no other. One in which only your skill can determine the outcome of the battle. Our team has learned and grown even more with familiar yet different gameplay mechanics including Single player (PVE) and Multiplayer (PVE &amp; PVP).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">When players first start the game, they will have to finish a training course to access other game modes. Players will be rewarded (token, NFT box) by completing it. After that, players will create their character (cost token or first one free), each player will have a maximum of 3 characters, each character will have energy and it will cost energy to play. Players will receive an NFT box to open and get a common weapon\\/ item to start their journey. Every day, players will have a daily task (For example 10 headshots, 1 assist, kill with shotguns, etc...), they should try to finish them and get the reward<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_keywords\":\"MetaStrike\",\"meta_description\":\"A blockchain-based role-play shooting game with a collection of weapons for players to equip, upgrade level to complete mission and earn NFT & tokens.\"}}',	'2022-07-21 17:22:41',	'2022-07-21 17:22:41'),
