(10,	72,	'Tinhvan Digital deploys HiFACE Facial Recognition solution at the Southern Power Corporation (EVN SPC)',	'Recently, Tinhvan Enterprise Digital Transformation Solutions Center (Tinhvan Digital – TVD) signed the contract of “Deploying software service of access control system by facial authentication_HiFACE” with the Southern Power Corporation (EVN SPC) – TVD’s first State-owned customer.',	'<p>Recently, Tinhvan Enterprise Digital Transformation Solutions Center (Tinhvan Digital &ndash; TVD) signed the contract of&nbsp;<strong>&ldquo;Deploying software service of access control system by facial authentication_HiFACE&rdquo;</strong>&nbsp;with the Southern Power Corporation (EVN SPC) &ndash; TVD&rsquo;s first State-owned customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to its compact size and aesthetics, HiFACE also has ability to integrate directly with the organization&rsquo;s timekeeping software, users absolutely do not have to carry any swipe card type. TVD&rsquo;s solution has ability to customize data reports based on the actual needs of customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The successful closing of the project with great value at the year end helps TVD take an important step on the runway &ldquo;Towards the Finish Line 2020&rdquo; when the signed sales have reached 76% of the plan. 2021 is a pivotal year for the Government&rsquo;s implementation of &ldquo;Digital Transformation&rdquo;. Therefore, the project with EVN SPC is considered as a favorable first step on the journey to realize the objectives that Tinhvan has set out.</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-05-27 13:37:55',	'2021-05-28 14:52:18',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
