(48,	97,	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'The client is one of the world’s largest consumer goods companies which is stablished over 100 years ago. They are known for great brands, a global footprint and belief in doing business the right way.',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>The Client</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The client is one of the world&rsquo;s largest consumer goods companies which is stablished over 100 years ago. They are known for great brands, a global footprint and belief in doing business the right way.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In order to track and manage the performance of their sales team across the Asia, client wants a comprehensive mobile application which is used by their salesmen to present the products, record the sales volume &amp; manage customers. The data from multiple countries is then centralized to a role-based portal for analytic purposes. This large-scaled solution has been developed by Tinhvan Software for 5 years and ongoing. It is rolled out in more than 20 countries globally with over 2,000 active users (which are salesmen &amp; sales leaders). Sales Tracker Solution is regarded one of the most successful projects TSO has been working on - receiving lots of credits from the client &amp; their users.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Solutions</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>TSO</em></strong> built up a team the team consists in 5 R&amp;D developers based in our headquarter. We work closely with the Client Service Team and the Infrastructure team to offer tech support and maintenance when needed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Benefit </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>For salesman</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Self-manage quota &amp; KPI</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Customers Management</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Product presentation and Ordering</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Data synchronization</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis report</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>For sales leader</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Set/approve/manage sales target/quota/plan</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis team reports</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>For CMS&nbsp;- a Role-based multi-country portal</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis Customer management</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sales performance tracking</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Product management</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Project Summary</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sales information management</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Performance Infographic</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Application Development both Front-end &amp; Back-end</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Maintain and update the application up to now</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Technologies&nbsp;Used&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">iOS, Android, PHP, .Net, Restful API, Bootstrap</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2021-06-09 16:33:08',	'2022-07-28 10:35:24',	'sales-tracker-solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'Meta Open Graph URL'),
