(187,	148,	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'<p><img alt=\"Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021\" src=\"/storage/files/News/Events/Tinh Van Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The year 2021 marks a big change for Tinhvan Software. The company changed its name from Tinhvan Software (TSO), a key unit in Tinhvan Group&#39;s Go Global strategy, to Tinhvan Software (TSO) not only providing Outsourcing services but also expanding its business activities in products digital transformation products and solutions for businesses with the Biz@DX solution suite.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In 2015, Tinhvan Software received the title of Vietnam&#39;s Leading IT Outsourcing Enterprise 2015 by the Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This year, Tinhvan Software was awarded Sao Khue Award in the field of software export services. This is the recognition of the BTC (Vinasa) as well as of the Vietnamese IT community for Tinhvan Software&#39;s contributions in the field of software outsourcing and exporting in recent years.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sao Khue Award is the most prestigious award in the field of software and IT services, held since 2003, accompanying the history of establishment and development of the Vietnam Association of Software and IT Services Enterprises. Vinasa and sponsored by the Ministry of Information and Communications.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This event was also reported by many prestigious newspapers such as VTV, Thanh Nien, etc., to congratulate Tinhvan Software for our efforts to achieve this accomplishment</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em>Photo: Mr. Bui Thanh Tung, director of BU2 - Tinhvan Software - received the Sao Khue 2022 award.</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:35:30',	'2022-07-28 14:20:17',	'tinhvan-software-received-the-sao-khue-award-2022-for-best-software-outsourcing-service-2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021'),
(188,	148,	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn',	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Năm 2021 đ&aacute;nh dấu một sự thay đổi lớn của Tinhvan Software. C&ocirc;ng ty đổi t&ecirc;n từ Tinhvan Software (TSO), đơn vị chủ lực trong chiến lược Go Global của Tinhvan Group, th&agrave;nh Tinhvan Software (TSO) kh&ocirc;ng chỉ cung cấp dịch vụ Gia c&ocirc;ng m&agrave; c&ograve;n mở rộng hoạt động kinh doanh ở c&aacute;c sản phẩm v&agrave; giải ph&aacute;p chuyển đổi số cho doanh nghiệp với Bộ giải ph&aacute;p Biz @ DX.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Năm 2015, <strong>Tinhvan Software </strong>nhận danh hiệu <strong><em>Doanh nghiệp Gia c&ocirc;ng CNTT </em></strong>H&agrave;ng đầu Việt Nam 2015 do Hội Tin học TP.HCM trao tặng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Năm nay, <strong>Tinhvan Software</strong> đ&atilde; được trao giải Sao Khu&ecirc; trong lĩnh vực dịch vụ xuất khẩu phần mềm. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; sự ghi nhận của BTC (Vinasa) cũng như của cộng đồng CNTT Việt Nam đối với những đ&oacute;ng g&oacute;p của Tinhvan Software trong lĩnh vực gia c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; xuất khẩu phần mềm trong thời gian qua.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong>Giải thưởng Sao Khu&ecirc;</strong></em> l&agrave; giải thưởng uy t&iacute;n nhất trong lĩnh vực phần mềm v&agrave; dịch vụ CNTT, được tổ chức từ năm 2003, đồng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng lịch sử h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển của Hiệp hội Doanh nghiệp phần mềm v&agrave; dịch vụ CNTT Việt Nam. Vinasa v&agrave; được sự bảo trợ của Bộ Th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; Truyền th&ocirc;ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sự kiện n&agrave;y cũng được nhiều trang b&aacute;o uy t&iacute;n như b&aacute;o VTV, B&aacute;o Thanh Ni&ecirc;n,&hellip; đưa tin v&agrave; ch&uacute;c mừng cho những nỗ lực của Tinhvan Software để đạt được th&agrave;nh tựu n&agrave;y.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html](https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm](https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Ảnh: &Ocirc;ng B&ugrave;i Thanh T&ugrave;ng, gi&aacute;m đốc BU2 - Tinhvan Software - nhận giải thưởng Sao Khu&ecirc; 2022.</span></em></p>',	'vi',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:35:30',	'2022-07-05 16:05:52',	'tinhvan-software-received-the-sao-khue-award-2022-for-best-software-outsourcing-service-2021-vn',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn'),
(189,	148,	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2021年は、<em><strong>TinhvanSoftware</strong></em>にとって大きな変化を迎えました。同社は、TinhvanGroupのGoGlobal戦略の主要ユニットであるTinhvanSoftware（TSO）から、アウトソーシングサービスを提供するだけでなく、製品デジタルトランスフォーメーション製品およびビジネス向けソリューションの事業活動を拡大するTinhvan Software（TSO）に社名を変更しました。 Biz@DXソリューションスイート。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2015年、<em><strong>Tinhvan Software</strong></em>は、ホーチミン市コンピュータ協会からベトナムの大手ITアウトソーシングエンタープライズ2015の称号を授与されました。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">今年、<em><strong>Tinhvan Software</strong></em>は、ソフトウェア輸出サービスの分野で<em><strong>SaoKhueAward</strong></em>を受賞しました。これは、近年のソフトウェアのアウトソーシングとエクスポートの分野でのTinhvan Softwareの貢献に対するBTC（Vinasa）とベトナムのITコミュニティの認識です。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sao Khue Awardは、ソフトウェアおよびITサービスの分野で最も権威のある賞であり、ベトナムソフトウェアおよびITサービス企業協会の設立と発展の歴史に伴い、2003年から開催されています。ビナサと情報通信省が後援。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">この度、ベトナムの大手VTVやBAO THANH NIEN 新聞社が取り上げて頂きました。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size:16px\">写真：BU2（Tinhvan Software）のディレクターであるBui Thanh Tung氏は、SaoKhue2022賞を受賞しました。</span></em></p>',	'ja',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:35:30',	'2022-07-12 