business needs and foster new innovative products and service and cater to changing business needs.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Business Transformation is the real change that is causing a storm in the business world. Its impact is felt not only in operations but also in industry structures and also at all levels in the organization. Business leaders and CIOs are coming forward to ensure that digital transformation coupled with innovation is driving business and bringing in productive changes and delivering value.</p>\n\n<p>Source: Forbes <a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianrashid/2017/06/13/digital-transformation-and-innovation-in-todays-business-world/?sh=3f6b09824905\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianrashid/2017/06/13/digital-transformation-and-innovation-in-todays-business-world/?sh=3f6b09824905</a></p>',	'vi',	1,	'2021-07-16 13:08:51',	'2021-07-16 13:08:51',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
