(689,	302,	'Budget Tool',	'Budget tool allows AEON Vietnam to streamline the annual budget planning process throughout their organization including departments and malls and provide targets that will help their business grow.',	'<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/budget tool.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Client:</strong> AEON Vietnam&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs: </strong>Budget tool allows AEON Vietnam to streamline the annual budget planning process throughout their organization including departments and malls and provide targets that will help their business grow. It also gives the Financial department the opportunity to stand back and review other performances and the factors affecting their business.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 years, 50MM</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Project Brief:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Develop a whole new website both front end &amp; back end and interface with SAP ERP system.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Maintain &amp; update the application up to now</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 10:43:02',	'2022-07-21 16:21:40',	'budget-tool',	'Budget Tool',	'Budget Tool',	'Budget tool allows AEON Vietnam to streamline the annual budget planning process throughout their organization including departments and malls and provide targets that will help their business grow.',	'Budget Tool'),
(690,	303,	'Construction',	'Construction is an useful application to manage track of projects and tasks, as well as the progress of them. It also serves as the communication channel between contractor with customers.',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Track list of projects (status, duration, to-do list, etc.)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Track and capture daily reports and weekly timesheets</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Easily and quickly manage quality control, safety and commissioning issues and expedite specific issues</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Collect customer feedback</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Technical detail</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">OS/ Environment: Android 4.0 and above&nbsp;</span></p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 10:48:04',	'2022-07-08 23:36:53',	'construction',	'Construction',	'Construction',	'Construction is an useful application to manage track of projects and tasks, as well as the progress of them. It also serves as the communication channel between contractor with customers.',	'Construction'),
