(756,	331,	'Sales Tracking Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution provides an effective tool that allows sales men & sales leaders to perform the selling as well as tracking the sales quota, for the purpose of increasing the sales of food products.',	'<h2><img alt=\"Sales Tracking Solution\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/Sale Tracking Solution.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs:</strong> </span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In order to track and manage the performance of their sales team across the Asia, client wants a comprehensive mobile application which is used by their salesmen to present the products, record the sales volume &amp; manage customers. The data from multiple countries is then centralized to a role-based portal for analytic purposes.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This large-scaled solution has been developed by Tinhvan Outsourcing for 5 years and ongoing. It is rolled out in more than 20 countries globally with over 2,000 active users (which are salesmen &amp; sales leaders). Sales Tracker Solution is regarded one of the most successful projects TSO has been working on - receiving lots of credits from the client &amp; their users.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Project Brief:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Application Development both Front-end &amp; Back-end</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Maintain and update the application up to now</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Main features:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong>For salesman:</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Self-manage quota &amp; KPI&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Customers Management&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Product presentation and Ordering&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Data synchronization&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis report&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong>For sales leader:</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Set/approve/manage sales target/quota/plan&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis team reports &nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">For CMS - a Role-based multi-country portal:</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Analysis Customer management&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sales performance tracking&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Product management&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sales information management&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Performance Infographic&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:44:13',	'2022-07-29 15:03:17',	'sales-tracking-solution',	'Sales Tracking Solution',	'Sales Tracking Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution provides an effective tool that allows sales men & sales leaders to perform the selling as well as tracking the sales quota, for the purpose of increasing the sales of food products.',	'Sales Tracker Solution'),
(757,	331,	'Giải pháp Theo dõi Bán hàng',	'Giải pháp Theo dõi Bán hàng cung cấp một công cụ hiệu quả cho phép nhân viên bán hàng và trưởng nhóm bán hàng thực hiện việc bán hàng cũng như theo dõi hạn ngạch bán hàng, nhằm mục đích tăng doanh số bán các sản phẩm thực phẩm.',	'<p><img alt=\"Giải pháp Theo dõi Bán hàng\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/Sale Tracking Solution.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhu cầu kinh doanh:<br />\r\nĐể theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; quản l&yacute; hoạt động của đội ngũ b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n ch&acirc;u &Aacute;, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng muốn c&oacute; một ứng dụng di động to&agrave;n diện được nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng của họ sử dụng để giới thiệu sản phẩm, ghi lại doanh số b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng v&agrave; quản l&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng. Dữ liệu từ nhiều quốc gia sau đ&oacute; được tập trung v&agrave;o một cổng th&ocirc;ng tin dựa tr&ecirc;n vai tr&ograve; cho c&aacute;c mục đ&iacute;ch ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch.<br />\r\nGiải ph&aacute;p quy m&ocirc; lớn n&agrave;y đ&atilde; được Tinhvan Outsourcing ph&aacute;t triển trong 5 năm v&agrave; vẫn đang tiếp tục. N&oacute; được triển khai tại hơn 20 quốc gia tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n cầu với hơn 2.000 người d&ugrave;ng đang hoạt động (l&agrave; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng &amp; l&atilde;nh đạo b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng). Giải ph&aacute;p Theo d&otilde;i B&aacute;n h&agrave;ng được coi l&agrave; một trong những dự &aacute;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nhất m&agrave; TSO đ&atilde; v&agrave; đang thực hiện - nhận được rất nhiều t&iacute;n dụng từ kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; người d&ugrave;ng của họ.<br />\r\nT&oacute;m tắt dự &aacute;n:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ph&aacute;t triển ứng dụng cả Front-end &amp; Back-end<br />\r\nDuy tr&igrave; v&agrave; cập nhật ứng dụng cho đến nay<br />\r\nNhững đặc điểm ch&iacute;nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đối với nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tự quản l&yacute; hạn ngạch &amp; KPI<br />\r\nQuản l&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nTr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y sản phẩm v&agrave; Đặt h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nĐồng bộ h&oacute;a dữ liệu<br />\r\nB&aacute;o c&aacute;o ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch<br />\r\nĐối với trưởng nh&oacute;m b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đặt / ph&ecirc; duyệt / quản l&yacute; mục ti&ecirc;u / hạn ngạch / kế hoạch b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nB&aacute;o c&aacute;o của nh&oacute;m ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch<br />\r\nĐối với CMS - cổng th&ocirc;ng tin đa quốc gia dựa tr&ecirc;n Vai tr&ograve;:<br />\r\nPh&acirc;n t&iacute;ch Quản l&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nTheo d&otilde;i hiệu suất b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nQuản l&yacute; sản phẩm<br />\r\nQuản l&yacute; th&ocirc;ng tin b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng<br />\r\nĐồ họa th&ocirc;ng tin về hiệu suất</p>',	'vi',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:44:13',	'2022-08-01 09:23:42',	'sales-tracking-solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution',	'Sales Tracker Solution provides an effective tool that allows sales men & sales leaders to perform the selling as well as tracking the sales quota, for the purpose of increasing the sales of food products.',	'Sales Tracker Solution'),
(758,	331,	'販売追跡ソリューション',	'クライアントは、100年以上前に設立された世界最大の消費財企業の1つです。彼らは素晴らしいブランド、グローバルな足跡、そして正しい方法でビジネスを行うという信念で知られています。',	'<h2><img alt=\"販売追跡ソリューション\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/Sale Tracking Solution.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>クライアント</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>クライアントは、100年以上前に設立された世界最大の消費財企業の1つです。彼らは素晴らしいブランド、グローバルな足跡、そして正しい方法でビジネスを行うという信念で知られています。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ビジネスニーズ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>アジア全体の営業チームのパフォーマンスを追跡および管理するために、クライアントは、営業担当者が製品の提示、販売量の記録、および顧客の管理に使用する包括的なモバイルアプリケーションを望んでいます。次に、複数の国からのデータが、分析目的で役割ベースのポータルに一元化されます。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>この大規模なソリューションは、TinhvanSoftwareによって5年間開発され続けています。世界20か国以上で展開され、2,000人を超えるアクティブユーザー（セールスマンとセールスリーダー）がいます。 Sales Tracker Solutionは、TSOが取り組んできた最も成功したプロジェクトの1つと見なされており、クライアントとそのユーザーから多くのクレジットを受け取ります。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ソリューション</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TSOは、本社に拠点を置く5人のR＆D開発者で構成されるチームを構築しました。クライアントサービスチームおよびインフラストラクチャチームと緊密に連携して、必要に応じて技術サポートとメンテナンスを提供します。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>機能</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>セールスマンの場合</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 自己管理クォータとKPI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 顧客管理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 製品のプレゼンテーションと注文</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- データ同期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 分析レポート</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>セールスリーダーの場合</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-販売目標/割り当て/計画の設定/承認/管理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-分析チームのレポート</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CMSの場合:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 役割ベースの多国間ポータル</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-分析顧客管理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-販売実績の追跡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-製品管理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>プロジェクトの概要</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-販売情報管理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-パフォーマンスインフォグラフィック</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-フロントエンドとバックエンドの両方のアプリケーション開発</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-これまでのアプリケーションの保守と更新</p>',	'ja',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:44:13',	'2022-08-01 09:22:44',	'sales-tracking-solution',	'販売追跡ソリューション',	'Sales Tracking Solution,販売追跡ソリューション',	'クライアントは、100年以上前に設立された世界最大の消費財企業の1つです。彼らは素晴らしいブランド、グローバルな足跡、そして正しい方法でビジネスを行うという信念で知られています。',	'販売追跡ソリューション'),
(759,	332,	'NubizKat',	'NubizKat is a mobile solution for product/service catalogs and presentations. NubizKat can be considered as an e-assistant of salesman to go to meeting with customers or tradeshow, events and other marketing purpose.',	'<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Why do you need NubizKat?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">NubizKat, which means cloud catalog in Latin, supports users to create their own catalog within seconds, in an easy, fast and simple way. This mobile application is featured with well-designed, professional-looking templates for users to choose from and use as a catalogue layout. Together with the information input, the company&rsquo;s brand and the superior characteristics of the product/ service can be highlighted for tradeshow, events display &amp; other marketing purpose. Once it is created, the information is always open to access anywhere &amp; anytime. Besides online mode, this mobile app being available in offline mode will empower you to do as much as possible.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This mobile solution is made with user-friendly interface, which comes in handy for either an expert or beginner when in need of presentation for your company&rsquo;s products. Your own content can be collected from cloud, put into the available optimal templates and ready for use.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">What make users love NubizKat?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">NubizKat provides full customization when the company&rsquo;s requirements have to be met. Users can add new, edit, manage, and update available catalogue, or corporate their own design with full support. Products are also classified into different categories, so that users are free to choose any template to their own likings &amp; suitability.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">For better illustration, many great effects are ready to be used. Catalogue output can be exported to PDF file and attached to email. Customers&rsquo; comments &amp; sales history management are also on display.</span></p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:46:02',	'2022-07-06 13:18:53',	'nubizkat',	'NubizKat',	'NubizKat',	'NubizKat is a mobile solution for product/service catalogs and presentations. NubizKat can be considered as an e-assistant of salesman to go to meeting with customers or tradeshow, events and other marketing purpose.',	'NubizKat'),
